        "description": "Detect AI tool ports listening on non-loopback interfaces. Use for shadow AI network exposure triage — identifies Ollama, LM Studio, vLLM, ComfyUI, vector databases, and other AI services bound to externally-reachable addresses on well-known AI ports.",
